Curebit,is,a,social,marketing,campaign,platform,that,enables,companies,to,get,their,customers,to,refer,their,friends,from,social,networking,services,to,purchase,their,products,or,services,The,Curebit,API,allows,developers,to,access,the,subscribe,function,in,Curebit,As,the,API,is,in,the,initial,stage,developers,are,asked,to,contact,Curebit,if,they,plan,on,using,the,API